    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Memento Dawn》是一款色彩缤纷的解谜游戏，玩家将通过操纵光影，协助小女孩找回自己的记忆。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >疗愈人心的解谜体验</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >跟随小女孩遨游美丽奇境、唤醒珍贵记忆，协助她解开其中暗藏的谜团。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2319360/extras/60b75e2a82eab7e6b8f8730276da1b5e.avif?t=1771925592\" width=610 height=267 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >简明无门槛的独创机制</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >操纵光与影，为女孩铺设穿越黑暗的道路。收集回忆，看可爱暖心的故事画卷徐徐展开。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2319360/extras/cc08df97ddec07fe4b9909f478fc80a1.poster.avif?t=1771925592\" width=600 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2319360/extras/cc08df97ddec07fe4b9909f478fc80a1.webm?t=1771925592\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2319360/extras/cc08df97ddec07fe4b9909f478fc80a1.mp4?t=1771925592\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >发现独特的机制，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2319360/extras/08f434c31c6072897189d3c369534424.poster.avif?t=1771925592\" width=600 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2319360/extras/08f434c31c6072897189d3c369534424.webm?t=1771925592\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2319360/extras/08f434c31c6072897189d3c369534424.mp4?t=1771925592\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >并在旅途中享受意想不到的惊喜。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2319360/extras/71eae7ea0fb49a7904fb54006dba13cc.poster.avif?t=1771925592\" width=600 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2319360/extras/71eae7ea0fb49a7904fb54006dba13cc.webm?t=1771925592\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2319360/extras/71eae7ea0fb49a7904fb54006dba13cc.mp4?t=1771925592\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色：</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 借助光影的独特玩法。 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 简明又不乏深度的游戏机制。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >内含提示系统，每一步操作均可撤回。 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 温馨可爱的故事情节，附带精美插画。 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 舒缓而抚慰人心的原声音乐。 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 可爱合家欢风格，适合所有玩家。 </p></li></ul>",
